not count as a surveyed household. Do not include this household in the survey sheet. Move to the next/adjacent house. After the survey is over, note down total number of such cases on the cover page of the survey booklet under 'no response households'.

---

1. Respondent = An adult who is present in the household during the survey and is providing the information.

